#to indicate a price in dollars. ''The total with tax is $1.05.''
#in certain computer languages (such as [[PHP]]) to indicate a [[variable]].
#in some computer languages it may be used to indicate a [[hexadecimal]] constant.
#in some computer languages it may be used to indicate a [[constant]].
#in certain computer languages (such as [[BASIC]]) to indicate a variable or a constant contains text (a ''[[string]]'') as opposed to a [[number]].

